steps.name: I see the Agent Contact Form from steaky header
I enter "Test Lead" in the steaky header form name field
I enter "FS_SRP_Sticky_H2@regression.com" in the steaky header form email field
I enter "1234567890" in the steaky header form phone field
I uncheck the improve your credit score box
I click the steaky header form submit button
I should see the myHomes Overlay Agent Card
I should see "Thank you for your interest in this property"

elements.name: Submitting A For Rent Request Info Property Lead form from steaky header

steps.name: I am on a For Rent details page
I click the Request Info Button on steaky header
I see the Agent Contact Form from steaky header
I enter "Test Lead" in the steaky header form name field
I enter "FS_SRP_Sticky_H1@regression.com" in the steaky header form email field
I enter "1234567890" in the steaky header form phone field
I click the submit button
I should see the myHomes Overlay Agent Card
I should see "Poor Credit Can Keep You From Getting The Home You Really Want!"

arguments.val: Poor Credit Can Keep You From Getting The Home You Really Want!

steps.name: I click the Submit button in the form
I should see the Lead Confirmation
I should see "Thank you for your interest in this property"
